{"tid":2018550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾批評無調查權 已辭職國際專家諷監警會報告傳達「新真相」 對林鄭「無言」","createTime":"2020-05-15T16:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T05:11:50.000Z","uid":201464,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"08395931b1dbba43b78028f7a4e3898c24137a82","tid":2018550,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hfspMc0LMOVxNNBGF0QRGC3diOjN-WCpfKQJoQxJaZ2g0VyoCcVVwMm40NG83Bn4CI1p_OGowIm0zUy5ZeFZw/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hfspMc0LMOVxNNBGF0QRGC3diOjN-WCpfKQJoQxJaZ2g0VyoCcVVwMm40NG83Bn4CI1p_OGowIm0zUy5ZeFZw%2Fw644&h=a346d25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n監警會今日發表審視反修例運動警方行動的報告，曾批評監警會「權力及獨立調查能力不足」、已退出其國際專家小組的英國基爾大學 (Keele University) 自然科學研究院院長 Clifford Stott，亦有關注報告內容，更在其個人Twitter 連番發文點評。他引述報告的多段內容，包括元朗 721 的相關部分，認為報告重覆了一種說法，認為公眾因 7.21 事件質疑警方的合法性，是基於誤解。他又引述名作家喬治奧威爾 (George Orwell) 的說話：「一個社會越遠離真相，越憎惡揭示真相的人」（the further the society drifts from the truth the more it will hate those who speak it），批評監警會的報告是要製造「新真相」。<br />\n<br />\n他在引述喬治奧威爾的說話時，加上評論，指監警會的報告似乎是一連串公布的一部分，用途是發放一個「新真相」。<br />\n   <br />\n It would seem the release of the IPCC report is part of a wider set of coordinated announcements designed to deliver the new 'truth'. <a href=\"https://t.co/xQ5n0UElMm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxQ5n0UElMm&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=9f97ce4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/xQ5n0UElMm</a> <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/bnsYZhBCmY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FbnsYZhBCmY&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=53f45a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/bnsYZhBCmY</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Clifford Stott (@cliffordstott) May 15, 2020<br />\n<br />\nClifford Stott 兩度提及元朗 721 事件，指監警會重覆了一種說法，認為公眾因 7.21 事件質疑警方的合法性，是基於誤解。<br />\n<br />\n    IPCC reproduces narrative that public view of police illegitimacy that grew from incidents on 21st July were based on misunderstanding.<br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Clifford Stott (@cliffordstott) May 15, 2020<br />\n<br />\n他亦引述有關新屋嶺收押的段落，報告內文指，有別其他警局的中央電腦系統，新屋嶺以人手處理記錄，而醫療要求等紀錄均不完整。<br />\n<br />\n監警會報告第 4 章又提及，在示威活動中，較激進示威者以 「Black Bloc」的策略，蒙面混入人群，藉此掩蓋身份，其他和平示威者同樣戴上口罩，亦會令他們感鼓舞，並視之為所給予的支持或後盾。Clifford Stott 則諷刺，監警會報告「有趣地」應用專家供詞，支持報告內「被扭曲」的去個體化理論，他又說，至今仍未找到當代的科學證據，去解讀人群的動態。<br />\n<br />\n他又轉發 Hong Kong Free Press 就行政長官林鄭月娥回應監警會報告的報導，再加上一句 「Speechless」 ( 無言 )。<br />\n<br />\nClifford Stott 是早前受邀加入國際五人專家小組其中一員，但去年 11 月，專家小組聯合發表聲明，稱監警會「權力及獨立調查能力不足」，認為有必要加強取證能力，才能完成臨時報告。到 12 月，5 名專家宣布集體請辭。惟監警會主席梁定邦當時否認專家組是辭職，指他們只是完成「階段性工作」後退出。<br />\n<br />\nClifford Stott 今日發的貼文中，亦有引述報告內所指，「監警會沒有調查權力，要求有關人士披露資料」的說法。<br />\n    Speechless! <a href=\"https://t.co/4QZ8aQeFIv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4QZ8aQeFIv&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=05cbde32\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/4QZ8aQeFIv</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; Clifford Stott (@cliffordstott) May 15, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/曾批評無調查權-已辭職國際專家諷監警會報告傳達-新真相-對林鄭-無言/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9B%BE%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%84%A1%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%AC%8A-%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%B7%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%82%B3%E9%81%94-%E6%96%B0%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8-%E5%B0%8D%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%80%2F&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=3135f807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9B%BE%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%84%A1%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%AC%8A-%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%B7%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%82%B3%E9%81%94-%E6%96%B0%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8-%E5%B0%8D%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%80%2F&h=e4caae26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/曾批評無調查權-已辭職國際專家諷監警會報告傳達-新真相-對林鄭-無言/</a>"},{"pid":"aa40441ed22c9b267c0fd55e957d7602f7010acf","tid":2018550,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"c52c4756df6fde41868d2ca0e95b74be585077c6","tid":2018550,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"f49a5290e3d5ad33828087c5ff09c41d489e3cfc","tid":2018550,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3840bf61b9ba05677dd69cae09dde203f8237d24","tid":2018550,"uid":39503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"記得click入去支持立場新聞"},{"pid":"b2201ca8f61531f3608717b1051a59151f32237e","tid":2018550,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"46be5840dc5fd551f36b8d04bf5bc8b86ec7dd2c","tid":2018550,"uid":62714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"一切都向著1984方向進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baee08f11125d39a79106bca22b6312a295c4ed0","tid":2018550,"uid":43381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7701f0c81fee93adf78ab549da89093fc783eb2a","tid":2018550,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T17:30:53.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"b1d2ce4b4a97e93def05911dfc1c72eac25e2bd1","tid":2018550,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:03:27.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"1f5906ffffa95f373e79c6d7add4cad4b3ba1f1e","ti